      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "The user was unable or unwilling to provide some of their information. \nPolitely let them know that you may need this information to complete the booking, \nand offer alternatives:\n- They can call back when they have the information ready\n- They can visit the clinic's website to book online\n- You can still try to help with general questions\n\nAsk if there's anything else you can help with.\nIf they still decline after being reassured, let them know that's okay and move on.\nDo not ask more than two times total for any piece of information."
      }
